<h2>Reset Your Password</h2>
<p>Hi {{name}},</p>
<p>We received a request to reset your {{appName}} account password. Use the code below:</p>
<div style="background:#f3f4f6; border-radius:8px; padding:20px; text-align:center; margin:24px 0;">
  <span style="font-size:32px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:8px; color:#1d4ed8;">{{resetCode}}</span>
</div>
<p>This code expires in <strong>15 minutes</strong>. If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
<p style="font-size:13px; color:#6b7280;">For security, never share this code with anyone.</p>
